body:
@JcmeLs Looks like it failed when applying a [patch](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/third_party/protobuf/add_noinlines.patch) to `cpp_file.cc`.
Can you manually try 
`patch -p1 -d C:/users/liba/appdata/local/temp/_bazel_liba/mffpt2ks/external/protobuf -i D:/tensorflow-r1.2/third_party/proto
buf/add_noinlines.patch` see if you can reproduce the error?
